  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cross-chain atomic swaps between EVM chains and Solana",
    "Hash-lock based escrow system for secure transfers",
    "Support for native and ERC-20 tokens",
    "Real-time order tracking via WebSocket",
    "Integrator fee collection",
    "Multiple execution presets (slow, fast, medium)",
    "Order cancellation and refunds",
    "TypeScript with full type safety"
